divs: Sighting Detailsdriving to work in lousia ky on old road 23 i observed a tube shaped objectcovered with reg lights coming down the rock wall fast then slow down,cross theroad and go into the big sandy river i thought it was a car wreck so i sloweddown and watched it go under the water all the time seeing the red lights underthe water then before it reached the otherside.it stopped in the water and satthere,then it disappeared.
